page.title: 16Tamsin Fielden's Day
page.content: My mum wakes me up early every morning so that I can feed the cats, chickens, ducks and geese.Then I have to help my sister let the horses out into the field.I go and help my dad milk and feed the cows.When I come back I ride my pony and then I groom her.After I have done that I have brunch.I have to help my mum do the house work and then I have some free time.I go and play at my friend's house and I come back in time to put the horses away and feed them and the cats and dogs.I have a bath and then go to bed and read for a while.
